<br>
I try to stand far from the mob, and I also try not to sit down right after i cast. Should i give up one of my spell slots for that aggro reducer spell we got? I forget its name. I only used it a couple of times and I never noticed a difference.<br>
<br>
Is this a CHA issue? Buffed, my CHA is usually around 217.<br>
<br>
Is it related to the quality of tanks I play with? I have noticed it happen in several different groups.<br>
<br>
Let me know if anyone else experiences this or if i should just shut up and deal with it.<br>
<br>
